parameters:
\TA[1](What is that, that person. A demon-like creature?) (No,
although I can sense a strange intention from them...)

\TA[1]...Either way, if they are the culprit of the disappearance
case, we can't let them get away.

\TA[1](...No, now that we know they're in the sewer, we can come
and exterminate them anytime.)
\TA[1](Today, let's let the underclassman go home first.)
\TA[1]Hehe... Senpai, do you prefer this? Ahn ♡

\TA[1]Ouch! Why are you hitting me?! Normally, you wake someone up
with a kiss, right?!
\TA[1]There's no way we would do it with each other.
\TA[1]Haa... Yes, hold on tight. I'll take you home safely.
\TA[1]Wow~ I love you so much, Senpai.
